title: Express+Storyblok starter
description: A customizable boilerplate on Express.js, tailored for Storyblok, AMP, Web Stories, and Schema.org. It's AMP-ready, ensuring optimal mobile performance. This starter simplifies development, making it easy to create high-performing web applications with Storyblok integration and enhanced search engine visibility through Schema.org.

title: JSON prefetch Nuxt module
description: Nuxt module designed to optimize performance by reducing network requests and mitigating unexpected API responses through static data prefetching.
